# §11.4.10 / §11.4.30 — ephemeral throwaway TEST key material is NOT tracked.
# gen_fixtures.sh regenerates everything on demand (§11.4.77 regen mechanism);
# only the PUBLIC *.pem certificates are committed as the golden fixtures.
*.key
*.csr
*.srl
# Intermediate wrong-issuer CA scaffolding: only the wrongca_leaf.pem it signs
# is a tracked fixture; the CA cert itself is regenerable scaffolding.
wrong_ca.pem
